Mechanical Maintenance Technician
SEOT
Location:
Dubai, Dubai
Date: 01-05-2014
Salary Details:
Competitive Package
Job Type: Employee
Job Status: Full Time
Categories:
Technical & Skilled
Oil & Gas
SEOT
Please see Job Details for Apply instructions
Saved!
Job Details
Work Experience:
Should have thorough knowledge of static and rotating equipment.
Should have basic knowledge of trouble shooting, dismantling and re-assembling of medium sized petroleum product pumps. ( Centrifugal pump, vertical turbine pump, double screw pump )
Should have knowledge of various types of couplings and expertise on rotating equipment coupling alignment
Should be well versed with various types of valves.
Should have a good knowledge of pipeline inspection and corrosion mapping methodology.
Should be well versed with preventive maintenance system and procedures.
Should know to handle vibration monitoring device like IRD / Vistec, tabulate and analyze the data for adopting appropriate corrective action.
Should have thorough knowledge of equipment isolation and tagging procedure.
Should be aware of basic safety rules and regulations followed in petroleum industries.
Requirements
Basic Requirements:
Qualification : Diploma in Mechanical engineering.
Age : 25 – 35 years.
Experience : 10 – 15 years.
IT skills : should have basic knowledge of computer, MS office.
Should be able to converse in English and write basic technical reports.
Kindly send your CV to:cv@seot.ae
